text: Parahepomidion granulatum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1908.BioLib.cz - Parahepomidion granulatum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1908
